85
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,888
-Sure.
-Okay.

86
00:10:38,972 --> 00:10:41,182
-Let's have a drink.
-Here.

87
00:10:44,352 --> 00:10:45,520
-Drink up, Sang-su.
-Drink up.

88
00:10:45,603 --> 00:10:47,856
