97
00:11:48,333 --> 00:11:51,419
What happened between her and me
has nothing to do with you.

98
00:12:06,851 --> 00:12:08,186
Then back then…

99
00:12:14,609 --> 00:12:17,570
why did you do that to me?

100
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,705
Why did you flinch?

101
00:12:30,458 --> 00:12:31,668
I didn't flinch.

102
00:12:31,751 --> 00:12:32,752
You just did.

103
00:12:35,546 --> 00:12:38,007
You always flinch more than I do
whenever that comes up.

104
00:12:47,725 --> 00:12:49,602
Whatever you do is your call…

105
00:12:52,271 --> 00:12:56,025
but I was in pain for a long time
because of what you did.

106
00:13:03,116 --> 00:13:05,201
I'm not asking
because I still have feelings.

107
00:13:07,203 --> 00:13:08,287
I just…

108
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:12,834
I've always wondered…

109
00:13:16,254 --> 00:13:18,131
what the reason was…

110
00:13:19,424 --> 00:13:20,717
for what you did.

111
00:13:40,611 --> 00:13:42,321
Because I liked you.

112
00:13:46,617 --> 00:13:47,577
But…

113
00:13:50,121 --> 00:13:52,415
