141
00:16:57,266 --> 00:16:59,101
-Congratulations!
-Great job.

142
00:16:59,185 --> 00:17:00,478
-My gosh.
-Hey!

143
00:17:00,561 --> 00:17:03,397
-Mr. Ma, congrats!
-Congratulations!

144
00:17:05,983 --> 00:17:07,777
