221
00:26:44,561 --> 00:26:45,979
<i>Are you sure about this?</i>

222
00:26:47,981 --> 00:26:49,483
<i>Yes.</i>

223
00:26:56,365 --> 00:26:58,909
-Did you listen to it?
-What are you doing?

224
00:26:58,992 --> 00:27:00,327
